Section 109(a) of the Legislative Branch Appropriations Act, 1998 (
  2 U.S.C. 95d(a)
) is amended by striking the period at the end and inserting the following: , and for reimbursing the Secretary of Labor for any amounts paid with respect to unemployment compensation payments for former employees of the House..


Section 1018 of the Legislative Branch Appropriations Act, 2003 (
  2 U.S.C. 1907
) is amended by striking subsection (f).
